Use the Artvendoor wordmark prominently in the hero.

## Rules
- never distort
- never rotate
- use approved palette only
- preserve whitespace
- premium spacing
- clean top-center or top-left placement

Recommended:
- white logo on dark hero overlay
- terracotta accent on “VENDOOR”

