# 10) Imagery Rules
Use:
- high-quality gallery photography
- installation shots
- framed art closeups
- artist studio moments
- neutral product imagery
- white space around visuals

Avoid:
- low-res art
- over-filtered images
- busy stock images
- random abstract SaaS illustrations

---

# 11) Animation Direction
Allowed:
- slow fade-up
- parallax image movement
- subtle zoom on hero artwork
- CTA hover elevation
- smooth countdown transitions

Avoid:
- excessive bouncing
- flashy motion
- distracting particle effects

Motion should feel like a gallery reveal.


---

# 13) Mobile UX Rules
On mobile:
- keep artwork face visible
- ensure overlay stronger
- maintain centered CTA
- countdown stacks cleanly
- large tap targets
- logo scales elegantly

The image focal point should remain on the face.

---

